My friend says it is a glich, but I think he is wrong. Please reply and say whether I am correct or not. If not, please tell me what is going on.

From a confused player.
snippet.textOriginal:

                      For me, the NPCs are not in my games and I cannot enter the vault. There is no boss in the new POIs and I cannot shake down knocked players.                                                                     From a confused player.
